M|Comm|tx|\| Mistake \| Fix \|
M|Comm|tx|\|---------\|-----\|
M|Comm|tx|\| Performative agreement \| State requirement or just act \|
M|Comm|tx|\| Blind implementation \| Verify against codebase first \|
M|Comm|tx|\| Batch w/o testing \| One at a time, tst each \|
M|Comm|tx|\| Assuming reviewer is right \| Check if breaks things \|
M|Comm|tx|\| Avoiding pushback \| tc correctness > comfort \|
M|Comm|tx|\| Partial implementation \| Clarify all items first \|
M|Comm|tx|\| Can't verify, proceed anyway \| State limitation, ask for direction \|
