M|GitH|tx|When replying to inline rv comments on GitHub, reply in the comment thread (`gh ap repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/{pr}/comments/{id}/replies`), not as a top-level PR comment.
M|The |tx|**External feedback = suggestions to evaluate, not orders to follow.**
M|The |tx|Verify. Question. Then im.
M|The |tx|No performative agreement. tc rigor always.